  "text": "Expression and purification of SRY was carried out as described by Murphy et al. [CITATION_1] . Samples of the complexes chelating Mn 2+ or Ca 2+ were prepared as described [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Data were recorded on 0.3 mM complex dissolved in 10 mM Tris-HCl (pH 6.8), 20 mM NaCl, and 7% D 2 O.",
